She saw Terrorsaur fall out of the sky. "Nooo!"
She watched as he hit ground.  She got up and limped over to him, 
leaving a fluid trail.  She fell at his side. "PLease get up 
Terrorsaur. You have to stay and fight. Please get up."
She hoped he wasn't dead.
